在[[拓樸學|拓樸學]]中，'''負維空間'''是將一般的空間[[維度|維度]]向[[負整數|負整數]]的拓展<ref name="Luke_Wolcott_Elizabeth_McTernan">{{cite conference | first1 = Luke | last1 = Wolcott | first2 = Elizabeth | last2 = McTernan | title = Imagining Negative-Dimensional Space | pages = 637-642 | book-title = Proceedings of Bridges 2012: Mathematics, Music, Art, Architecture, Culture | year = 2012 | editor-first1 = Robert | editor-last1 = Bosch | editor-first2 = Douglas | editor-last2 = McKenna | editor-first3 = Reza | editor-last3 = Sarhangi | isbn = 978-1-938664-00-7 | issn = 1099-6702 | publisher = Tessellations  Publishing | location = Phoenix, Arizona, USA | url = http://bridgesmathart.org/2012/cdrom/proceedings/65/paper_65.pdf | accessdate = 25 June 2015 | archive-date = 2015-06-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150626111631/http://bridgesmathart.org/2012/cdrom/proceedings/65/paper_65.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>，表示一個[[維度|維度]]比[[零維空間|零維空間]]還要低的空間。例如在{{link-en|抽象多胞形|Abstract_polytope|抽象理論}}中，以[[負一維空間|負一維空間]]來表示維度比[[零維空間|零維]]還小的[[空多胞形|空多胞形]]。除了負一維，當然也能有負二、負三甚至更低的[[維度|維]]，而[[維度|維度]]在此就不能解釋為是[[數學|數學]]中[[参数|獨立參數]]的數目，而是[[拓樸|拓樸]]空間維度於[[負數|負數]]的推廣<ref>{{cite journal | author = В. П. Маслов | title = Отрицательная асимптотическая топологическая размерность, новый конденсат и их связь с квантованным законом Ципфа | journal = Матем. заметки | date = 2006-11-01 | volume = 80 | issue = 6 | pages = 806–813 | url = http://www.mathnet.ru/php/archive.phtml?wshow=paper&jrnid=mzm&paperid=3362&option_lang=rus | accessdate = 2016-08-03 | doi = 10.4213/mzm3362 | archive-date = 2021-02-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210226161200/http://www.mathnet.ru/php/archive.phtml?wshow=paper&jrnid=mzm&paperid=3362&option_lang=rus | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 定義 ==
假設{{math|''M''<sub>''t''<sub>0</sub></sub>}}是{{math|''t''<sub>0</sub>}}[[郝斯多夫維|郝斯多夫維數]]的[[紧空间|紧空间]]且是互相嵌入的緊空間元素並令參數t為[[零|零]]到[[無限|無限]]（{{math|0 < ''t'' < ∞}}）。若緊空間中構成這些元素都是{{math|''t'' ≥ ''t''<sub>0</sub>}}時，這個尺度就能視為與{{math|''M''<sub>''t''<sub>0</sub></sub>}}等價。這時就可以說[[紧空间|紧空间]]{{math|''M''<sub>''t''<sub>0</sub></sub>}}是這個尺度等價[[集合|集合]]的洞，而{{math|−''t''<sub>0</sub>}}是對應的等價類的負數維度<ref>{{cite journal|url=https://static-content.springer.com/lookinside/art%3A10.1134%2FS0001434607010166/000.png|doi=10.1134/S0001434607010166|title=General Notion of a Topological Space of Negative Dimension and Quantization of Its Density|journal=Mathematical Notes|volume=81|pages=140|year=2007|last1=Maslov|first1=V. P.|accessdate=2015-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626145228/https://static-content.springer.com/lookinside/art%3A10.1134%2FS0001434607010166/000.png|date=2006-12-6|archive-date=2015-06-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
1940年代時，[[拓撲|拓撲]]結構科學已有相當程度的發展，對於[[維度|正維度]]拓樸空間基本理論的研究也十分完備。在數值計算和一定程度美學的動機下，拓樸學家開始尋找能擴展空間概念、允許[[負數|負數]]維度的數學框架。但這樣的維度就像四維和更高的維度難以想像也無法直接觀察。直到1960年代時才建構了一個特殊的拓樸框架，即拓樸譜學的範疇。拓樸譜學是允許負維空間的一般化。負維空間的概念已經有實際用途了，如分析{{link-en|語言科學|Outline of linguistics|語言統計學}}<ref>{{cite web |url = http://arxiv.org/abs/math/0612543 |title = Negative Dimension in General and Asymptotic Topology |publisher = arxiv.org |accessdate = 2015-06-25 |first = V.P. |last = Maslov |archive-date = 2019-12-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191202144347/https://arxiv.org/abs/math/0612543 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

